<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idbf687ce3-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idbf687ce4-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1990-10-01">Oct. 1, 1990</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/101/501/s1001/a">section 1001(a) of Pub. L. 101–501</ref>, set out as an Effective Date of 1990 Amendment note under <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s8621">section 8621 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
